          The track where this note is contained. Might be null.

        • pan

          int pan
          CC 10 0x0a (coarse) 0 = left 64 = center 127 = right most devices ignore fine. Pan should effect all notes on the channel, including notes that were triggered prior to the pan message being received, and are still sustaining.

        • voice

          int voice
          not exactly midi
